HEADWORD: loanblend
<hw>loan"blend</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a word that is composed of parts
from different languages; e.g. <examp>monolingual</examp> has a Greek
prefix and a Latin root.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> hybrid.</syn>⟦br⟧
